---
description: Testing strategies and best practices for ensuring code quality and reliability.
alwaysApply: false
---

- All code must have corresponding tests.
- Achieve at least 80% code coverage for all critical modules.
- All UI components must have snapshot tests.
- Use data-testid attributes for testing selectors.
- Run tests in parallel to speed up CI.
- All tests must pass before merging.
- Use mocks/stubs for external dependencies in tests.
